snippet.title: Heal The Survivors - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Heal The Survivors is a horde survival game, where survival means staying awake, while trying to heal as many patients as possible. Collect coins to buy upgrades, advancing thru multiple incidents, crewmembers, and difficulties, using a wide assortment of tools and skills. 

Wherever people are hurt, or sickness is spreading, you've got to Heal The Survivors!

android https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.goodguydev.healthesurvivors
